---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout>
    <main class="p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">Collaborators</h1>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            The AURA Protocol was conceived, authored, and maintained by <strong>Fausto David Cortés Rojas</strong>, M.Sc., currently a PhD candidate in engineering sciences. His academic contributions are registered under <a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5224-5710" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ORCID 0000-0001-5224-5710</a>.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            This work integrates independent research, metadata modeling, and interface development to promote transparency, attribution, and reproducibility in AI-assisted content generation.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            The protocol structure, JSON schema, and documentation are designed and maintained as part of an academic initiative to establish a verifiable framework for acknowledging generative AI tools in scholarly and digital contexts.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">
            This site is hosted at <strong>aura.org</strong> and serves as a reference for the continued evolution of the AURA standard.
        </p>
    </main>
</Layout>
